# Peperoncini jam

* * 800g of peperoni rossi*
* * 200g of peperoncini*
* * 500g of sugar*
* * 50ml of red wine*
* * salt*

- remove the seed from the peperoncini
- dice all the vegetables 
- put everything into a put and cook for 1 hour
- pass everything to the vegetable mill 
- cook again for 10 minutes until it thickens. 
